reviewText:
Controls do not feel good to use as setup and can not be reconfigured.  The ship is extremely difficult to control.  You can not use a Gamepad or Joystick with this game.  I feel like I paid too much at $0.33.

Controls-
W, A, S, D to steer;
C, V for accelection;
R, F for rolling;
Shift for rear view;
1, 2, 3 for camera;
Mouse for aiming;
Left Mouse Button to fire
